snippet.title: Johnny Depp's cut finger after hearing Amber Heard had affair with Billy Bob Thronton
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp sliced off tip of his finger and wrote allegations of affair in his own Blood

Heard, 30, claims that Depp cut off the tip in a fit of rage and then used his blood to write words on the wall accusing her of having an affair
